Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Experience the thrills of racing round your favourite track in this officially licensed FIA grand prix simulation.

All the usual race types are here including championship, time trial, single race and practice mode. Choose your team and race the full season of the F1 calendar to become world champion.

As you would expect with a F1 game, all aspects of your game are customisable from laps, weather conditions and
pit stops to make this challenge more interesting. All the car set-ups can be changed to make you the fastest on
track.

And the other drivers will keep you on your toes cause the AI of the other drivers wont make it easy. No dumb Sunday drivers in this game, they all want to win so make sure your car setup is right and take the championship.